name: Gainos studio
body:
Welcome to GaInOS.
    GaInOS is developed according to the standard OSEK and Autosar OS specification.
    It's free and published according to GPL.
    This is GaInOS Studio which will configure the kernel GaInOS include Tasks,alarms,counters and so on.
    The kernel GaInOS is at [GaInOS kernel](http://parai.github.com/GaInOS/).
